      "created": "2017-02-23T06:32:19.057+0000",
      "description": "In situation like YARN-6101, if we consider all type of resource(vcore, memory) utilization on node rather than just answer we can allocate or not, we are more likely to have better resource utilization as a whole.\nIt is possible that we have a set of candidate nodes, then find the most promising node to assign to one request considering node resource utilization with global scheduling.",
